#. <section class="sutta" id="an8.72"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an8.72:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 8"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 8"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.72:0.2"
msgid "8. Yamakavagga"
msgstr "8. Pairs"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an8.72:0.3"
msgid "72. Dutiyasaddhāsutta"
msgstr "72. Inspiring All Around (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an8.72:1.1"
msgid "“Saddho ca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu hoti, no ca sīlavā."
msgstr "“A mendicant is faithful, but not ethical."

msgctxt "an8.72:1.2"
msgid "Evaṃ so tenaṅgena aparipūro hoti."
msgstr "So they’re incomplete in that respect,"

msgctxt "an8.72:1.3"
msgid "Tena taṃ aṅgaṃ paripūretabbaṃ:"
msgstr "and should fulfill it, thinking:"

msgctxt "an8.72:1.4"
msgid "‘kintāhaṃ saddho ca assaṃ sīlavā cā’ti."
msgstr "‘How can I become faithful and ethical?’"

msgctxt "an8.72:1.5"
msgid "Yato ca kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu saddho ca hoti sīlavā ca, "
msgstr "When the mendicant is faithful and ethical, "

msgctxt "an8.72:1.6"
msgid "evaṃ so tenaṅgena paripūro hoti."
msgstr "they’re complete in that respect."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.316"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an8.72:2.1"
msgid "Saddho ca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu hoti sīlavā ca, no ca bahussuto … pe …"
msgstr "A mendicant is faithful and ethical, but not learned. …"

msgctxt "an8.72:2.2"
msgid "bahussuto ca, no ca dhammakathiko … pe …"
msgstr "they’re not a Dhamma speaker …"

msgctxt "an8.72:2.3"
msgid "dhammakathiko ca, no ca parisāvacaro … pe …"
msgstr "they don’t frequent assemblies …"

msgctxt "an8.72:2.4"
msgid "parisāvacaro ca, no ca visārado parisāya dhammaṃ deseti … pe …"
msgstr "they don’t teach Dhamma to the assembly with assurance …"

msgctxt "an8.72:2.5"
msgid ""
"visārado ca parisāya dhammaṃ deseti, no ca ye te santā vimokkhā atikkamma "
"rūpe āruppā te kāyena phusitvā viharati … pe …"
msgstr ""
"they don’t have direct meditative experience of the peaceful liberations "
"that are formless, transcending form …"

msgctxt "an8.72:2.6"
msgid ""
"ye te santā vimokkhā atikkamma rūpe āruppā te kāyena phusitvā viharati, no "
"ca āsavānaṃ khayā anāsavaṃ cetovimuttiṃ paññāvimuttiṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ "
"abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharati;"
msgstr ""
"they don’t realize the undefiled freedom of heart and freedom by wisdom in "
"this very life, and live having realized it with their own insight due to "
"the ending of defilements."

msgctxt "an8.72:2.7"
msgid "evaṃ so tenaṅgena aparipūro hoti."
msgstr "So they’re incomplete in that respect,"

msgctxt "an8.72:2.8"
msgid "Tena taṃ aṅgaṃ paripūretabbaṃ:"
msgstr "and should fulfill it, thinking:"

msgctxt "an8.72:2.9"
msgid ""
"‘kintāhaṃ saddho ca assaṃ, sīlavā ca, bahussuto ca, dhammakathiko ca, "
"parisāvacaro ca, visārado ca parisāya dhammaṃ deseyyaṃ, ye te santā vimokkhā "
"atikkamma rūpe āruppā te kāyena phusitvā vihareyyaṃ, āsavānañca khayā "
"anāsavaṃ cetovimuttiṃ paññāvimuttiṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā "
"sacchikatvā upasampajja vihareyyan’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘How can I become faithful, ethical, and learned, a Dhamma speaker, one who "
"frequents assemblies, one who teaches Dhamma to the assembly with assurance, "
"one who gets the formless liberations, and one who lives having realized the "
"ending of defilements?’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an8.72:3.1"
msgid ""
"Yato ca kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu saddho ca hoti, sīlavā ca, bahussuto ca, "
"dhammakathiko ca, parisāvacaro ca, visārado ca parisāya dhammaṃ deseti. Ye "
"te santā vimokkhā atikkamma rūpe āruppā te ca kāyena phusitvā viharati, "
"āsavānañca khayā … pe … sacchikatvā upasampajja viharati;"
msgstr ""
"When they’re faithful, ethical, and learned, a Dhamma speaker, one who "
"frequents assemblies, one who teaches Dhamma to the assembly with assurance, "
"one who gets the formless liberations, and one who lives having realized the "
"ending of defilements,"

msgctxt "an8.72:3.2"
msgid "evaṃ so tenaṅgena paripūro hoti."
msgstr "they’re complete in that respect."

msgctxt "an8.72:3.3"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, aṭṭhahi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu samantapāsādiko "
"ca hoti sabbākāraparipūro cā”ti."
msgstr ""
"A mendicant who has these eight qualities is inspiring all around, and is "
"complete in every aspect.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an8.72:3.4"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
